{"id":24730426859,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAFwgxd6w","head_branch":"fix_missing_name_oauth2_clients","head_sha":"41bfa275b279bb4349a83b6442d40edb11cb4714","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":49169,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: OAuth2 client list endpoint failing when sorting by name","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":65553960301,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAPQ1INbQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24730426859","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24730426859","pull_requests":[{"id":3557540505,"number":23666,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/23666","head":{"ref":"fix_missing_name_oauth2_clients","sha":"f4dbe84b720b5f182ca08dcf952db54ba67f7d39","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"62c1f5a6a2b88ab8ebfabf82ed3f3bf0946236df","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-04-21T15:14:25Z","updated_at":"2026-04-21T15:27:05Z","run_started_at":"2026-04-21T15:14:25Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24730426859/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24730426859/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/65553960301","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24730426859/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24730426859/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24730426859/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix(sec): make name nullable, deny dangerous redirect URI schemes, truncate\n\nFixes from security review:\n\n1. Make `name` nullable (hbm not-null=\"false\", migration drops NOT NULL\n   from the single ALTER). The settings UI has no name field and POSTs\n   to /api/schemas/oAuth2Client for pre-validation, which calls the\n   schema validator directly and bypasses the controller hook. When hbm\n   marks name required, every UI-driven create fails at pre-validation\n   with E4000 before the controller can default it. The controller still\n   defaults name = clientId on the real save path.\n\n2. Deny-list known dangerous schemes (javascript, data, vbscript, file,\n   about, blob, jar, view-source, ws, wss) in validateRedirectUris.\n   Spring Authorization Server does exact-string matching of the stored\n   redirect URI and then emits a Location header with no scheme\n   filtering, so a stored `javascript:alert(document.cookie)` would\n   execute in the victim's browser after a completed authorize flow.\n   Custom native-app schemes (dhis2oauth://, com.dhis2.app://) are still\n   accepted.\n\n3. Truncate the default name to 230 chars (NAME_MAX_LENGTH). clientId\n   is varchar(255); persisted name is varchar(230); without truncation\n   a long clientId would throw a DB `value too long` exception.\n\n4. Migration backfill uses `substring(client_id, 1, 230)` to guard\n   against the same length mismatch on existing rows.\n\nTests added: javascript:/data:/file: rejection, long-clientId name\ntruncation, schema-endpoint acceptance without name.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"41bfa275b279bb4349a83b6442d40edb11cb4714","tree_id":"71c56cd70dba1d7a5352f0e12a836b800631d7f6","timestamp":"2026-04-21T15:14:14Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","